lubs.\n\nA meeting with club officials on December 23 had agreed to resume the league, halted since March 18, 2020, due to the coronavirus pandemic, from February 23.","title":"ANFA allows five substitutes for \u2018B\u2019 Division League - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2021/04/154083/","video":[]}
